## Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Patches don't apply cleanly to 10.47.0 | Regenerate fresh — patches are purely subtractive |
| `_INTERNAL_safeUnref` stripped by core patch | Verify it's preserved (it's in a different section than stripped exports) |
| `monitorEventLoopDelay` unavailable in Bun | Built-in try/catch in the integration — degrades gracefully |
| 5s timer overhead | Negligible; timer is unref'd so it won't keep process alive |
| Breaking changes in 10.45-10.47 | Check release notes for 10.45.0, 10.46.0, 10.47.0 for any breaking changes |
